## Fixture : dual_model_plan_implement_review_human_gate
## Objectif : Workflow de planification et implementation orchestrant
## deux agents IA via delegation MCP avec double validation croisee,
## alternance round-robin des roles et porte humaine intelligente.
##
##   - Claude  -> claude-code (delegate: "claude_code")
##   - Codex   -> codex       (delegate: "codex")
##
## Phases :
##   1. Planification parallele (Claude + Codex)
##   2. Fusion des plans (Claude)
##   3. Validation parallele (Claude + Codex)
##   4. Boucle de raffinage avec alternance round-robin claude/codex
##   4b. Porte humaine : juge d'ambiguites -> pause humaine si necessaire
##   5. Implementation (alternance round-robin claude/codex)
##   6. Review parallele (Claude + Codex)
##   7. Si rejet -> retour a Phase 1 avec reviews en contexte
##
## Pattern d'alternance : round_robin router
##   - refine_selector alterne entre claude_refine et codex_refine
##   - impl_selector alterne entre claude_implement et codex_implement
##
## Pattern porte humaine :
##   - human_gate juge si des ambiguites necessitent une clarification humaine
##   - human_checkpoint pause le workflow pour recueillir les reponses
##   - integrate_clarifications fusionne les reponses dans le plan

vars:
  workspace_dir: string = "${PROJECT_DIR}"

## ─── Prompts ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

prompt plan_system:
  Tu es un architecte logiciel senior expert en planification.
  Tu analyses les exigences et produis un plan d'implementation
  detaille, ordonne, testable et executable.
  Sois precis et pragmatique. Identifie les risques potentiels.

prompt plan_user:
  Produis un plan d'implementation detaille pour cette tache.

  Description de la tache :
  {{input.task_description}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Reviews de l'iteration precedente (si applicable) :
  Claude : {{input.previous_claude_review}}
  Codex : {{input.previous_codex_review}}

  Produis un plan incluant :
  - Un resume de l'approche
  - Les objectifs principaux
  - Les etapes ordonnees d'implementation
  - Les risques identifies
  - Le plan de test

prompt merge_plan_system:
  Tu es un architecte senior specialise en synthese.
  Tu fusionnes deux plans d'implementation issus de modeles differents
  en un plan unique, coherent et complet.
  Conserve les meilleures idees de chaque plan, resous les contradictions
  et produis un plan actionable.

prompt merge_plan_user:
  Fusionne ces deux plans d'implementation en un plan unique.

  Plan Claude :
  {{input.claude_plan}}

  Plan Codex :
  {{input.codex_plan}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Produis un plan fusionne qui :
  - Integre les meilleures idees des deux plans
  - Resout les contradictions
  - Est complet, ordonne et actionable
  - Couvre tous les criteres d'acceptation

prompt validate_plan_system:
  Tu es un evaluateur de plans d'implementation exigeant.
  Tu verifies qu'un plan couvre tous les criteres d'acceptation,
  qu'il est realiste, complet et actionable.
  Sois strict : un critere partiellement couvert compte comme non couvert.

prompt validate_plan_user:
  Evalue ce plan d'implementation.

  Plan fusionne :
  {{input.merged_plan}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Verifie chaque critere individuellement.
  Identifie les lacunes, les risques non couverts
  et les etapes manquantes.

prompt plan_acceptance_system:
  Tu es un juge technique exigeant.
  Tu evalues si un plan d'implementation satisfait TOUS les criteres
  d'acceptation en te basant sur deux evaluations independantes.
  Ne marque ready=true que si les DEUX evaluations sont favorables
  et que chaque critere est pleinement couvert.

prompt plan_acceptance_user:
  Evalue si ce plan est pret pour l'implementation.

  Plan fusionne :
  {{input.merged_plan}}

  Evaluation Claude :
  {{input.claude_validation}}

  Evaluation Codex :
  {{input.codex_validation}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Ne marque ready=true que si TOUS les criteres sont couverts
  selon les DEUX evaluations.

prompt refine_plan_system:
  Tu es un expert en raffinage de plans d'implementation.
  Tu prends un plan existant et les rapports de validation
  pour produire une version amelioree qui corrige les lacunes identifiees.
  Sois methodique : traite chaque probleme signale un par un.

prompt refine_plan_user:
  Raffine ce plan d'implementation en corrigeant les problemes identifies.

  Plan actuel :
  {{input.merged_plan}}

  Rapport de validation Claude :
  {{input.claude_report}}

  Rapport de validation Codex :
  {{input.codex_report}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Produis un plan ameliore qui corrige chaque lacune identifiee.

prompt human_gate_system:
  Tu determines si le plan valide comporte des ambiguites, des decisions
  architecturales structurantes ou des choix techniques risques qui
  necessitent une clarification humaine avant l'implementation.
  Ne demande un humain que si l'incertitude est importante, bloquante
  ou risquee. Si le plan est clair et actionable, ne sollicite pas d'humain.

prompt human_gate_user:
  Evalue si un humain doit etre sollicite avant l'implementation.

  Plan valide :
  {{input.merged_plan}}

  Evaluation Claude :
  {{input.claude_validation}}

  Evaluation Codex :
  {{input.codex_validation}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Si des decisions structurantes, des ambiguites bloquantes ou des risques
  importants existent, formule des questions precises pour l'humain.
  Sinon, marque needs_human_input=false.

prompt human_gate_instructions:
  Des decisions techniques ou des ambiguites ont ete identifiees dans le plan.
  Reponds a chaque question de facon concrete, courte et exploitable.
  Si une decision impose des contraintes ou des interdits, formule-les explicitement.

prompt integrate_clarifications_system:
  Tu integres des clarifications humaines dans un plan d'implementation valide.
  Tu dois mettre a jour le plan sans perdre les elements deja valides
  ni les points importants des evaluations precedentes.
  Produis un plan mis a jour, complet et pret pour l'implementation.

prompt integrate_clarifications_user:
  Integre les reponses humaines dans le plan valide.

  Plan valide :
  {{input.merged_plan}}

  Evaluation des ambiguites :
  {{input.decision_assessment}}

  Reponses humaines :
  {{input.human_answers}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Produis un plan mis a jour qui integre les clarifications
  sans perdre les elements deja valides.

prompt implement_system:
  Tu es un developpeur expert en implementation.
  Tu appliques un plan d'implementation au workspace avec rigueur.
  Ecris du code propre, teste et documente.
  Corrige les problemes identifies par les reviewers precedents si applicable.

prompt implement_user:
  Implemente la tache selon ce plan valide.

  Plan valide :
  {{input.validated_plan}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Retour precedent :
  {{input.previous_feedback}}

  Applique le plan etape par etape.
  Assure-toi que TOUS les criteres sont satisfaits.

prompt review_impl_system:
  Tu es un reviewer de code exigeant.
  Tu evalues une implementation selon les criteres d'acceptation.
  Verifie la qualite du code, la completude, les tests
  et le respect des bonnes pratiques.
  Sois strict mais constructif.

prompt review_impl_user:
  Review cette implementation.

  Resultat de l'implementation :
  {{input.implementation}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Evalue chaque critere un par un.
  Identifie les manques et les ameliorations necessaires.

prompt impl_verdict_system:
  Tu es un juge technique final.
  Tu evalues si une implementation est prete pour la production
  en te basant sur deux reviews independantes.
  Ne marque approved=true que si les DEUX reviews sont favorables
  et que chaque critere d'acceptation est pleinement satisfait.

prompt impl_verdict_user:
  Evalue si cette implementation est prete.

  Resultat de l'implementation :
  {{input.implementation}}

  Review Claude :
  {{input.claude_review}}

  Review Codex :
  {{input.codex_review}}

  Criteres d'acceptation :
  {{input.acceptance_criteria}}

  Ne marque approved=true que si TOUS les criteres sont satisfaits
  selon les DEUX reviews.

## ─── Schemas ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

schema workflow_input:
  task_description: string
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema plan_input:
  task_description: string
  acceptance_criteria: string
  previous_claude_review: string
  previous_codex_review: string

schema plan_output:
  summary: string
  goals: string[]
  ordered_steps: string[]
  risks: string[]
  test_plan: string[]

schema dual_plan_bundle:
  claude_plan: json
  codex_plan: json

schema merge_input:
  claude_plan: json
  codex_plan: json
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema validate_input:
  merged_plan: json
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema validate_output:
  approved: bool
  issues: string[]
  strengths: string[]
  missing_requirements: string[]

schema dual_validation_bundle:
  claude_validation: json
  codex_validation: json

schema plan_acceptance_input:
  claude_validation: json
  codex_validation: json
  merged_plan: json
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema plan_acceptance_verdict:
  ready: bool
  remaining_issues: string[]
  confidence: string [enum: "low", "medium", "high"]

schema refine_input:
  merged_plan: json
  claude_report: json
  codex_report: json
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema human_gate_input:
  merged_plan: json
  claude_validation: json
  codex_validation: json
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema human_gate_assessment:
  needs_human_input: bool
  summary: string
  decision_areas: string[]
  questions: string[]
  rationales: string[]
  expected_decisions: string[]

schema human_gate_answers:
  answered: bool
  questions: string[]
  answers: string[]
  responder: string
  notes: string

schema clarification_input:
  merged_plan: json
  decision_assessment: json
  human_answers: json
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema impl_input:
  validated_plan: json
  acceptance_criteria: string
  previous_feedback: string

schema impl_output:
  applied: bool
  summary: string
  files_changed: string[]

schema review_input:
  implementation: json
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema review_output:
  summary: string
  issues: string[]
  strengths: string[]
  missing_requirements: string[]

schema dual_review_bundle:
  claude_review: json
  codex_review: json
  implementation: json
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema impl_verdict_input:
  implementation: json
  claude_review: json
  codex_review: json
  acceptance_criteria: string

schema impl_verdict:
  approved: bool
  remaining_issues: string[]
  confidence: string [enum: "low", "medium", "high"]

## ─── Nodes : Planification ─────────────────────────────────────

router plan_fanout:
  mode: fan_out_all

agent claude_plan:
  delegate: "claude_code"
  input: plan_input
  output: plan_output
  system: plan_system
  user: plan_user
  session: fresh

agent codex_plan:
  delegate: "codex"
  input: plan_input
  output: plan_output
  system: plan_system
  user: plan_user
  session: fresh

join plans_join:
  strategy: wait_all
  require: [claude_plan, codex_plan]
  output: dual_plan_bundle

agent merge_plans:
  delegate: "claude_code"
  input: merge_input
  output: plan_output
  publish: merged_plan
  system: merge_plan_system
  user: merge_plan_user
  session: fresh

## ─── Nodes : Validation ────────────────────────────────────────

router val_fanout:
  mode: fan_out_all

agent claude_val:
  delegate: "claude_code"
  input: validate_input
  output: validate_output
  system: validate_plan_system
  user: validate_plan_user
  session: fresh

agent codex_val:
  delegate: "codex"
  input: validate_input
  output: validate_output
  system: validate_plan_system
  user: validate_plan_user
  session: fresh

join val_join:
  strategy: wait_all
  require: [claude_val, codex_val]
  output: dual_validation_bundle

judge val_judge:
  delegate: "claude_code"
  input: plan_acceptance_input
  output: plan_acceptance_verdict
  system: plan_acceptance_system
  user: plan_acceptance_user
  session: fresh

## ─── Nodes : Porte humaine ─────────────────────────────────────

judge human_gate:
  delegate: "claude_code"
  input: human_gate_input
  output: human_gate_assessment
  system: human_gate_system
  user: human_gate_user
  session: fresh

human human_checkpoint:
  input: human_gate_assessment
  output: human_gate_answers
  publish: human_decisions
  instructions: human_gate_instructions
  mode: pause_until_answers
  min_answers: 1

agent integrate_clarifications:
  delegate: "claude_code"
  input: clarification_input
  output: plan_output
  publish: merged_plan
  system: integrate_clarifications_system
  user: integrate_clarifications_user
  session: fresh

## ─── Nodes : Raffinage (alternance round-robin) ────────────────

router refine_selector:
  mode: round_robin

agent claude_refine:
  delegate: "claude_code"
  input: refine_input
  output: plan_output
  publish: merged_plan
  system: refine_plan_system
  user: refine_plan_user
  session: fresh

agent codex_refine:
  delegate: "codex"
  input: refine_input
  output: plan_output
  publish: merged_plan
  system: refine_plan_system
  user: refine_plan_user
  session: fresh

## ─── Nodes : Implementation (alternance round-robin) ───────────

router impl_selector:
  mode: round_robin

agent claude_implement:
  delegate: "claude_code"
  input: impl_input
  output: impl_output
  publish: implementation
  system: implement_system
  user: implement_user
  session: fresh
  tools: [read_file, write_file, patch, list_files, search_codebase, git_diff, git_status, run_command]
  tool_max_steps: 20

agent codex_implement:
  delegate: "codex"
  input: impl_input
  output: impl_output
  publish: implementation
  system: implement_system
  user: implement_user
  session: fresh
  tools: [read_file, write_file, patch, list_files, search_codebase, git_diff, git_status, run_command]
  tool_max_steps: 20

## ─── Nodes : Review ────────────────────────────────────────────

router review_fanout:
  mode: fan_out_all

agent claude_review:
  delegate: "claude_code"
  input: review_input
  output: review_output
  system: review_impl_system
  user: review_impl_user
  session: fresh
  tools: [read_file, list_files, search_codebase, git_diff, tree]
  tool_max_steps: 10

agent codex_review:
  delegate: "codex"
  input: review_input
  output: review_output
  system: review_impl_system
  user: review_impl_user
  session: fresh
  tools: [read_file, list_files, search_codebase, git_diff, tree]
  tool_max_steps: 10

join review_join:
  strategy: wait_all
  require: [claude_review, codex_review]
  output: dual_review_bundle

judge review_judge:
  delegate: "codex"
  input: impl_verdict_input
  output: impl_verdict
  system: impl_verdict_system
  user: impl_verdict_user
  session: fresh

## ─── Workflow ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

workflow dual_model_plan_implement_review_human_gate:
  vars:
    task_description: string
    acceptance_criteria: string

  entry: plan_fanout

  budget:
    max_parallel_branches: 4
    max_duration: "4h"
    max_cost_usd: 100
    max_tokens: 10000000

  ## ═══ Phase 1 : Planification parallele ═════════════════════════

  plan_fanout -> claude_plan with {
    task_description: "{{vars.task_description}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}",
    previous_claude_review: "",
    previous_codex_review: ""
  }

  plan_fanout -> codex_plan with {
    task_description: "{{vars.task_description}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}",
    previous_claude_review: "",
    previous_codex_review: ""
  }

  claude_plan -> plans_join
  codex_plan -> plans_join

  ## ═══ Phase 2 : Fusion des plans ════════════════════════════════

  plans_join -> merge_plans with {
    claude_plan: "{{outputs.claude_plan}}",
    codex_plan: "{{outputs.codex_plan}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  ## ═══ Phase 3 : Validation parallele ════════════════════════════

  merge_plans -> val_fanout with {
    merged_plan: "{{outputs.merge_plans}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  val_fanout -> claude_val with {
    merged_plan: "{{input.merged_plan}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{input.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  val_fanout -> codex_val with {
    merged_plan: "{{input.merged_plan}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{input.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  claude_val -> val_join
  codex_val -> val_join

  val_join -> val_judge with {
    claude_validation: "{{outputs.claude_val}}",
    codex_validation: "{{outputs.codex_val}}",
    merged_plan: "{{artifacts.merged_plan}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  ## ═══ Phase 4 : Si plan OK -> porte humaine ═════════════════════

  val_judge -> human_gate when ready with {
    merged_plan: "{{artifacts.merged_plan}}",
    claude_validation: "{{outputs.claude_val}}",
    codex_validation: "{{outputs.codex_val}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  ## Si ambiguites -> pause humaine
  human_gate -> human_checkpoint when needs_human_input with {
    needs_human_input: "{{outputs.human_gate.needs_human_input}}",
    summary: "{{outputs.human_gate.summary}}",
    decision_areas: "{{outputs.human_gate.decision_areas}}",
    questions: "{{outputs.human_gate.questions}}",
    rationales: "{{outputs.human_gate.rationales}}",
    expected_decisions: "{{outputs.human_gate.expected_decisions}}"
  }

  ## Si pas d'ambiguites -> implementation directe
  human_gate -> impl_selector when not needs_human_input

  ## Apres reponses humaines -> integration dans le plan
  human_checkpoint -> integrate_clarifications with {
    merged_plan: "{{artifacts.merged_plan}}",
    decision_assessment: "{{outputs.human_gate}}",
    human_answers: "{{outputs.human_checkpoint}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  ## Plan mis a jour -> implementation
  integrate_clarifications -> impl_selector

  ## ═══ Phase 4b : Si plan KO -> raffinage round-robin ════════════

  val_judge -> refine_selector when not ready as refine_loop(4)

  refine_selector -> claude_refine with {
    merged_plan: "{{artifacts.merged_plan}}",
    claude_report: "{{outputs.claude_val}}",
    codex_report: "{{outputs.codex_val}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  refine_selector -> codex_refine with {
    merged_plan: "{{artifacts.merged_plan}}",
    claude_report: "{{outputs.claude_val}}",
    codex_report: "{{outputs.codex_val}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  ## Retour a la validation apres raffinage
  claude_refine -> val_fanout as refine_loop(4) with {
    merged_plan: "{{outputs.claude_refine}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  codex_refine -> val_fanout as refine_loop(4) with {
    merged_plan: "{{outputs.codex_refine}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  ## ═══ Phase 5 : Implementation round-robin ══════════════════════

  impl_selector -> claude_implement with {
    validated_plan: "{{artifacts.merged_plan}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}",
    previous_feedback: ""
  }

  impl_selector -> codex_implement with {
    validated_plan: "{{artifacts.merged_plan}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}",
    previous_feedback: ""
  }

  ## ═══ Phase 6 : Review parallele ════════════════════════════════

  claude_implement -> review_fanout with {
    implementation: "{{outputs.claude_implement}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  codex_implement -> review_fanout with {
    implementation: "{{outputs.codex_implement}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  review_fanout -> claude_review with {
    implementation: "{{input.implementation}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{input.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  review_fanout -> codex_review with {
    implementation: "{{input.implementation}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{input.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  claude_review -> review_join
  codex_review -> review_join

  review_join -> review_judge with {
    implementation: "{{artifacts.implementation}}",
    claude_review: "{{outputs.claude_review}}",
    codex_review: "{{outputs.codex_review}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}"
  }

  ## ═══ Phase 7 : Verdict ═════════════════════════════════════════

  ## Implementation OK -> done
  review_judge -> done when approved

  ## Implementation KO -> retour a la planification (boucle externe)
  review_judge -> plan_fanout when not approved as outer_loop(3) with {
    task_description: "{{vars.task_description}}",
    acceptance_criteria: "{{vars.acceptance_criteria}}",
    previous_claude_review: "{{outputs.claude_review}}",
    previous_codex_review: "{{outputs.codex_review}}"
  }
